    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420060/extras/89e679f865fdf6470a933778ae903476.poster.avif?t=1769520495\" width=616 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420060/extras/89e679f865fdf6470a933778ae903476.webm?t=1769520495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420060/extras/89e679f865fdf6470a933778ae903476.mp4?t=1769520495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Candle》是一款冒险游戏，内含极具挑战性的谜题。你将在游戏中扮演 Teku 这一角色，他是个毫无经验的新手，而他所在的部落的萨满法师落入了邪恶的 Wakcha 部落魔掌之中，为了拯救萨满法师，他踏上了危险的旅程。但是，途中遍布邪恶的陷阱和困难险阻。若要克服这些挑战，你需要有敏锐的觉察力，也要对周围环境有良好的感知力，不然你迈出的下一步就可能是你的最后一步。<br><br>但 Teku 有一个独特的天赋：他的左手是一根蜡烛。让这根蜡烛成为一个明亮的灯塔，驱走你的敌人或照亮黑暗之地。<br><br>华丽的手绘水彩画面让《Candle》别具风情，所有的背景和角色的每幅画稿均经过精心绘制、扫描。游戏从始至终都会让你感觉这是一部灵动的绘画作品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420060/extras/c00effc176d5961879d084a690500919.poster.avif?t=1769520495\" width=616 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420060/extras/c00effc176d5961879d084a690500919.webm?t=1769520495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420060/extras/c00effc176d5961879d084a690500919.mp4?t=1769520495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>注意到所有的细节，解开极具挑战性的谜题<br></li><li>时刻保持警惕，下一个陷阱随时等你入坑<br></li><li>你的手中掌控着火焰的力量<br></li><li>手绘的水彩画面，栩栩如生<br></li><li>极富南美风情的华美原声音乐</li></ul>",
